#: ../physics.rst:389
msgid "Navigation Meshes"
msgstr "导航网格"

#: ../physics.rst:391
msgid ""
"Navigation meshes (commonly abbreviated *navmeshes*) are mesh objects that are "
"used to make pathfinding simpler by eliminating the need for additional "
"calculations such as collisions."
msgstr ""
"导航网格 (通常缩写 *navmeshes*) 是用来消除需要额外计算比如碰撞等使寻路更加简便的"
"网格物体。"

#: ../physics.rst:397
msgid ""
"In this example (taken from Code Snippets), navigation mesh is used to build a "
"path through the labyrinth."
msgstr "在此示例中 （取自代码片段），导航网格用于生成通过迷宫的路径。"

#: ../physics.rst:400
msgid "Creating Navigation Meshes"
msgstr "创建导航网格"

#: ../physics.rst:402
msgid ""
"To make a navmesh out of an object, turn on the ``Object Physics`` parameter on "
"the ``Physics`` panel and select ``Navigation Mesh`` from the ``Physics Type`` "
"list."
msgstr ""
"若要将物体生成 navmesh，打开 ``Physics`` 面板的 ``Object Physics`` 参数 ，从 "
"``Physics Type`` 列表中选择 ``Navigation Mesh`` 。"

#: ../physics.rst:408
msgid ""
"Navigation meshes can either be created manually or generated automatically "
"using a specific tool."
msgstr "导航网格也可以使用特定的工具手动创建或生成自动。"

#: ../physics.rst:415
msgid "This tool is native to Blender and not a part of the Blend4Web engine."
msgstr "此工具是原产于Blender并不是 Blend4Web 引擎的一部分。"

#: ../physics.rst:417
msgid ""
"This Navigation Mesh generation interface can be found on a dedicated panel "
"under the ``Scene`` tab, but, as this feature is intended for real-time "
"applications, it only appears if the Engine type is set to ``Blend4Web`` or "
"``Blender Game`` (Blender Internal, Cycles or any other rendering engine won’t "
"do)."
msgstr ""
"此导航网格生成接口可以发现专用面板下的 ``Scene`` 选项卡上，但此功能是为了实时应"
"用程序，它仅音引擎类型设置为  ``Blend4Web`` 或  ``Blender Game`` 才显示（Blender"
"内部、 Cycles 或任何其他渲染引擎不会有显示）。"

#: ../physics.rst:419
msgid ""
"The main tool on this panel is the ``Build Navigation Mesh`` button. As the "
"title suggests, it is used for building navigation meshes based on the "
"currently selected object. The navmesh is created as a separate object placed "
"above the selected object, thus leaving that object intact."
msgstr ""
"在此面板上的主要工具是  ``Build Navigation Mesh`` 按钮。正如标题所暗示的它用来建"
"设基于当前选定对象的导航网格。Navmesh 是作为一个单独的物体放置在所选的物体上面，"
"因此保留该物体创建的。"

#: ../physics.rst:421
msgid ""
"Aside from this button, the ``Navigation Mesh`` panel offers users several "
"groups of parameters to fine-tune the navmesh that will be generated."
msgstr ""
"除了此按钮  ``Navigation Mesh`` 面板为用户提供了几组参数将生成 navmesh 进行微"
"调。"

#: ../physics.rst:423
msgid "``Rasterization`` group of parameters:"
msgstr "``Rasterization`` （栅格化）组的参数︰"

#: ../physics.rst:426
msgid "*Cell Size*"
msgstr "*Cell Size*"

#: ../physics.rst:426
msgid ""
"Rasterized cell size. Greater values lead to bigger navmesh polygons. The "
"highest possible value is 1.0. Default value is 0.3."
msgstr ""
"栅格化单元格大小。更大的值会导致更大的 navmesh 多边形。最高的可能值是 1.0。默认"
"值为 0.3。"

#: ../physics.rst:429
msgid "*Cell Height*"
msgstr "*Cell Height*"

#: ../physics.rst:429
msgid ""
"Rasterized cell height (the distance between the navmesh and the object from "
"which it was generated). Default value is 0.2."
msgstr "栅格单元格高度 （navmesh 和生成它的对象之间的距离）。默认值为 0.2。"

#: ../physics.rst:431
msgid "``Agent`` group of parameters:"
msgstr "``Agent`` 组的参数︰"

#: ../physics.rst:434
msgid "*Height*"
msgstr "*Height*"

#: ../physics.rst:434
msgid "Minimum height where the agent can still walk. Default value is 2.0."
msgstr "最小高度，代理还能走路。默认值为 2.0。"

#: ../physics.rst:437
msgid "*Radius*"
msgstr "*Radius*"

#: ../physics.rst:437
msgid "The radius of the agent. Default value is 0.6."
msgstr "代理的半径。默认值为 0.6。"

#: ../physics.rst:440
msgid "*Max Slope*"
msgstr "*Max Slope*"

#: ../physics.rst:440
msgid ""
"Maximum angle of a slope agent can walk on. Measured in degrees. Default value "
"is 45."
msgstr "代理能够行走的坡度的最大角度。以度为单位。默认值为 45。"

#: ../physics.rst:443
msgid "*Max Climb*"
msgstr "*Max Climb*"

#: ../physics.rst:443
msgid ""
"The maximum height between grid cells the agent can climb. Default value is 0.9."
msgstr "网格单元格之间的最大高度，代理可以爬上。默认值为 0.9。"

#: ../physics.rst:445
msgid "``Region`` group of parameters:"
msgstr "``Region`` 组的参数︰"

#: ../physics.rst:448
msgid "*Min Region Size*"
msgstr "*Min Region Size*"

#: ../physics.rst:448
msgid ""
"The minimum size of a region (smaller regions will be deleted). Default value "
"is 8.0."
msgstr "一个区域的最小大小 （较小的区域将被删除）。默认值为 8.0 级。"

#: ../physics.rst:451
msgid "*Merged Region Size*"
msgstr "*Merged Region Size*"

#: ../physics.rst:451
msgid ""
"The minimum size of a region (smaller regions will be merged). Default value is "
"20.0."
msgstr "一个区域的最小大小 （较小的地区，将合并）。默认值为 20.0。"

