msgid "The method used to partition the navigation mesh. Supported methods are:"
msgstr "用于分区导航网格的方法。受支持的方法是︰"

#: ../physics.rst:456
msgid ""
"``Monotone`` is the fastest method. Using it may generate long thin polygons."
msgstr "``Monotone`` 是最快的方法。使用它可以生成细细长长的多边形。"

#: ../physics.rst:458
msgid ""
"``Layers`` — a slower, but still reasonably fast method that produces better "
"triangulations than Monotone partitioning."
msgstr ""
"``Layers`` —  速度较慢，但仍然相当快的方法，可产生更好的三角剖分比单调"
"（Monotone ）分区。"

#: ../physics.rst:460
msgid ""
"``Watershed`` — classic Recast partitioning method that generates the nicest "
"tessellation. This option is selected by default."
msgstr "``Watershed`` — 经典重铸生成最好的剖分分区方法。此选项是默认选中的。"

#: ../physics.rst:462
msgid "``Polygonization`` group of parameters:"
msgstr "``Polygonization`` 组的参数︰"

#: ../physics.rst:465
msgid "*Max Edge Length*"
msgstr "*Max Edge Length*"

#: ../physics.rst:465
