#: ../physics.rst:468
msgid "*Max Edge Error*"
msgstr "*Max Edge Error*"

#: ../physics.rst:468
msgid ""
"The maximum error of the distance from the contour to the cells. Default value "
"is 1.3."
msgstr "从轮廓到单元格的距离最大误差。默认值为 1.3。"

#: ../physics.rst:471
msgid "*Verts Per Poly*"
msgstr "*Verts Per Poly*"

